data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom home in Zebulon features guest bedroom down with full bath, kitchen with granite counter tops, tile backsplash and breakfast bar, living area with gas fireplace, front room can be formal dining or office, all LVP flooring and crown molding downstairs plus molding accents through out. Upstairs features oversized master with vaulted ceiling, spacious master bath and large closet plus 3 spacious guest bedrooms, a full bath, and laundry. Backyard is fenced and has oversized patio. Plus 2 car garage.
